  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Assessing App Requirements**\n\nI\'m evaluating the parameters of \"Community Hero.\" I\'m focused on the constraints and assessing the application\'s components: an Angular frontend, a NestJS backend, and PostgreSQL database using Cloud SQL, while incorporating Drizzle\'s skills related to pgsql, SQL, and relational databases.\n\n\n**Clarifying the Approach**\n\nI\'m now prioritizing understanding the user\'s immediate intent, which appears to be feature prioritization rather than direct implementation. There\'s a slight confusion, as the prompt seems to blend two distinct voices. I\'m focusing on clarifying whether a discussion phase is desired before development or a direct implementation is needed. Also, I\'m checking the file system for the available development environment details.\n\n\n**Verifying Framework Compatibility**\n\nI\'ve confirmed the initial `package.json` suggests a React/Vite/Express environment, which conflicts with the requested Angular/NestJS stack. I\'m reassessing whether the framework is intended to be the same, or if the user\'s intent to switch frameworks mid-plan is a possibility. I\'m considering if I can build a strong React/Express application integrating Gemini\'s AI features within the given environment.\n\n\n**Evaluating Skill Utilization**\n\nI\'ve shifted focus to verifying the skills within the existing React/Vite/Express environment. I\'ve conducted a \"Skill Check,\" and relevant skills include `cloudsql-setup`, `cloudsql-execute-sql`, `cloudsql-update-schema`, and `gemini-api`. I\'ll implement a secure, JWT-based authentication system backed by PostgreSQL, since OAuth is not specifically requested. I\'ve set up plans to use standard Tailwind for visual styling instead of shadcn-ui since it wasn\'t requested.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will read the Cloud SQL setup skill documentation to understand how to configure and provision a PostgreSQL database in this environment."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 4
      nanos: 683351573
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
