  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing the Dashboard**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the main Dashboard component\'s structure. It will feature several panels tailored to the user\'s role. For residents, I\'m imagining a clean, intuitive form for reporting issues. The form will feature an AI audit to help users provide good information.\n\n\n**Developing New Features**\n\nI\'ve been fleshing out the new resident features. The resident issue submission form will include an \"AI Analyzer\" button, providing a live preview of category, severity, and repair suggestions based on the user\'s input. Additionally, I\'m designing a community issues list with filtering and a verification system. Also in planning are a notification bell and a monthly feedback survey. For contractors, there\'s an active job feed and a bidding/assignment workflow in progress.\n\n\n**Analyzing Payment System**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the payments portal within the Elected Official/Administrator mode. I can now display resolved jobs with approved payouts. I\'m structuring a \"Release Payment\" button to payout contractors after admin review.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 94
      nanos: 113812900
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
