  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"High Density\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: High Density\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"bg-slate-50 w-[1024px] h-[768px] flex flex-col font-sans overflow-hidden text-slate-900\\\">\\n  <!-- Header: Civic Status Bar -->\\n  <header class=\\\"h-14 bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-between px-6 shrink-0 shadow-lg z-10\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500 rounded flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg\\\">C</div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"font-bold text-xl tracking-tight\\\">COMMUNITY<span class=\\\"text-emerald-400\\\">HERO</span></h1>\\n      <span class=\\\"ml-4 px-2 py-0.5 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Admin Terminal v2.4</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Civic Trust Score</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm font-bold\\\">84.2%</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-right border-l border-slate-700 pl-4\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Active Responders</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm font-bold\\\">128</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 border-l border-slate-700 pl-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600\\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-xs\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"font-semibold\\\">Officer Jenkins</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Central District</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"flex flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Sidebar Navigation -->\\n    <nav class=\\\"w-16 bg-slate-100 border-r border-slate-200 flex flex-col items-center py-4 gap-6 shrink-0\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-2 bg-white rounded shadow-sm border border-slate-300 text-slate-600\\\">\360\237\227\272\357\270\217</div>\\n      <div class=\\\"p-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 cursor-pointer\\\">\360\237\223\212</div>\\n      <div class=\\\"p-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 cursor-pointer\\\">\360\237\221\245</div>\\n      <div class=\\\"p-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 cursor-pointer\\\">\360\237\233\240\357\270\217</div>\\n      <div class=\\\"p-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 cursor-pointer\\\">\360\237\224\224</div>\\n      <div class=\\\"mt-auto p-2 text-slate-400\\\">\342\232\231\357\270\217</div>\\n    </nav>\\n\\n    <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <!-- Top Dashboard Grid -->\\n      <section class=\\\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-1 p-2 bg-slate-200 border-b border-slate-300 shrink-0\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white p-3 border border-slate-300\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Open Tickets</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono\\\">1,248</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-1 h-1 bg-slate-100 rounded overflow-hidden\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-full bg-red-500 w-[72%]\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] mt-1 text-red-600\\\">+12% from last week</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white p-3 border border-slate-300\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Avg. Response Time</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono\\\">4.2h</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-1 h-1 bg-slate-100 rounded overflow-hidden\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-full bg-emerald-500 w-[88%]\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] mt-1 text-emerald-600\\\">-15m improved</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white p-3 border border-slate-300\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Community Validation</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono\\\">92%</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-1 h-1 bg-slate-100 rounded overflow-hidden\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-full bg-blue-500 w-[92%]\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] mt-1 text-blue-600 text-right\\\">4,821 verification votes</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white p-3 border border-slate-300\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Contractor Efficiency</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono\\\">76.8</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-1 h-1 bg-slate-100 rounded overflow-hidden\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-full bg-amber-500 w-[76%]\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] mt-1 text-amber-600\\\">Target: 80.0</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n\\n      <!-- Main Workspace -->\\n      <section class=\\\"flex-1 flex overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <!-- Left: Issue Feed -->\\n        <div class=\\\"w-[380px] border-r border-slate-300 bg-white flex flex-col shrink-0\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"p-3 border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 flex justify-between items-center shrink-0\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-700\\\">LIVE INCIDENTS (24)</span>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex gap-1\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-red-100 text-red-700 text-[10px] rounded border border-red-200\\\">CRITICAL</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 text-[10px] rounded\\\">FILTER</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden space-y-[1px] bg-slate-200\\\">\\n            <!-- Card Item -->\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-3 border-b border-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-1\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400\\\">ID: #4092-B</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-[9px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\\\">HIGH SEVERITY</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight\\\">Water Leakage: Main Rd 45</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-1 line-clamp-1\\\">Significant wastage near community park hydrants.</p>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-2\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-1\\\">\342\217\263 <span class=\\\"font-mono\\\">3h 12m</span></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-1\\\">\360\237\221\244 <span class=\\\"font-mono text-slate-600 underline\\\">H. No 124</span></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-600 font-bold ml-auto\\\">Assigned</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <!-- Card Item -->\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-slate-50 p-3 border-b border-emerald-500 border-l-4 border-l-emerald-500\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-1\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400\\\">ID: #4095-C</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"bg-red-100 text-red-700 text-[9px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\\\">CRITICAL</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight\\\">Streetlight Failure: Sector 12</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-1\\\">Complete blackout over 4 blocks. Safety concern.</p>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-2\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-1\\\">\342\217\263 <span class=\\\"font-mono\\\">1h 05m</span></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-1\\\">\360\237\221\244 <span class=\\\"font-mono\\\">H. No 32-A</span></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-red-600 font-bold ml-auto animate-pulse\\\">Unattended</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n             <!-- Card Item -->\\n             <div class=\\\"bg-white p-3 border-b border-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer opacity-60\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-1\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400\\\">ID: #4088-A</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-[9px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\\\">LOW</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight\\\">Waste Management Overflow</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-1\\\">Bin full near secondary gate entrance.</p>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-2\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-1\\\">\342\217\263 <span class=\\\"font-mono\\\">18h 44m</span></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-1\\\">\360\237\221\244 <span class=\\\"font-mono\\\">H. No 92</span></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-bold ml-auto\\\">Validated</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n             <!-- Card Item -->\\n             <div class=\\\"bg-white p-3 border-b border-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer opacity-60\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-1\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400\\\">ID: #4080-X</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-[9px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\\\">MEDIUM</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight\\\">Pothole: Greenway Lane</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-1\\\">Deep crack causing tire damage risk.</p>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-2\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-1\\\">\342\217\263 <span class=\\\"font-mono\\\">2d 12h</span></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-1\\\">\360\237\221\244 <span class=\\\"font-mono\\\">H. No 15</span></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-bold ml-auto\\\">In Review</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Right: Detail & Analytics -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col bg-slate-50\\\">\\n          <!-- Mini Map Section -->\\n          <div class=\\\"h-48 bg-slate-300 m-4 rounded border border-slate-400 relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n             <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 opacity-40 bg-[radial-gradient(#000_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:20px_20px]\\\"></div>\\n             <div class=\\\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/3 w-4 h-4 bg-red-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white shadow-lg animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n             <div class=\\\"absolute top-1/4 right-1/4 w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white shadow-lg\\\"></div>\\n             <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white shadow-lg\\\"></div>\\n             <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur px-2 py-1 rounded border border-slate-300 text-[9px] font-bold\\\">Central District - Realtime View</div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Bottom Sections Grid -->\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 px-4 pb-4\\\">\\n            <!-- Contractor Board -->\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded border border-slate-300 flex flex-col overflow-hidden\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"px-3 py-2 border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase text-slate-600\\\">Local Contractors</span>\\n                <button class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-white border border-slate-300 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">View All</button>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-auto\\\">\\n                <table class=\\\"w-full text-[11px]\\\">\\n                  <thead class=\\\"bg-slate-50 text-slate-500 uppercase text-[9px] text-left border-b border-slate-200 sticky top-0\\\">\\n                    <tr>\\n                      <th class=\\\"p-2\\\">Name</th>\\n                      <th class=\\\"p-2\\\">Specialty</th>\\n                      <th class=\\\"p-2\\\">Active</th>\\n                      <th class=\\\"p-2\\\">Rating</th>\\n                    </tr>\\n                  </thead>\\n                  <tbody class=\\\"divide-y divide-slate-100\\\">\\n                    <tr>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 font-bold\\\">Apex Plumbing</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 text-slate-500\\\">Hydraulics</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2\\\">4</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 text-emerald-600 font-bold\\\">4.9/5</td>\\n                    </tr>\\n                    <tr>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 font-bold\\\">BrightLite Co.</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 text-slate-500\\\">Electrical</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2\\\">2</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 text-emerald-600 font-bold\\\">4.7/5</td>\\n                    </tr>\\n                    <tr>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 font-bold\\\">RoadSafe Inc.</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 text-slate-500\\\">Paving</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2\\\">8</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 text-amber-600 font-bold\\\">3.8/5</td>\\n                    </tr>\\n                    <tr>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 font-bold\\\">GreenWaste Ltd.</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 text-slate-500\\\">Waste</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2\\\">12</td>\\n                      <td class=\\\"p-2 text-emerald-600 font-bold\\\">4.5/5</td>\\n                    </tr>\\n                  </tbody>\\n                </table>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Resident Wellbeing Survey Insights -->\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded border border-slate-300 flex flex-col p-4 space-y-4\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase text-slate-600\\\">Wellbeing Survey (Monthly)</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400\\\">Oct 2023</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n                <div>\\n                  <div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-[11px] mb-1\\\">\\n                    <span>Infrastructure Satisfaction</span>\\n                    <span class=\\\"font-mono font-bold\\\">68%</span>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-full\\\">\\n                    <div class=\\\"h-full bg-amber-400 rounded-full w-[68%]\\\"></div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <div>\\n                  <div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-[11px] mb-1\\\">\\n                    <span>Response Time Sentiment</span>\\n                    <span class=\\\"font-mono font-bold\\\">82%</span>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-full\\\">\\n                    <div class=\\\"h-full bg-emerald-500 rounded-full w-[82%]\\\"></div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <div>\\n                  <div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-[11px] mb-1\\\">\\n                    <span>Security Awareness</span>\\n                    <span class=\\\"font-mono font-bold\\\">54%</span>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-full\\\">\\n                    <div class=\\\"h-full bg-slate-400 rounded-full w-[54%]\\\"></div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\\"bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-100 p-2 rounded\\\">\\n                <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-indigo-700 leading-tight italic\\\">\\\"Citizens reporting high satisfaction in water management but growing concern over streetlight delay in Sector 12.\\\"</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n    </main>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <!-- Footer: Meta Information -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-6 bg-slate-100 border-t border-slate-300 flex items-center justify-between px-4 shrink-0 text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono uppercase\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <span>DB STATUS: CONNECTED (POSTGRESQL-PROD)</span>\\n      <span>UPTIME: 99.98%</span>\\n      <span>ENCRYPTION: AES-256-GCM</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <span>SYSTEM TIME: 14:22:51 UTC</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"text-emerald-600\\\">\342\227\217 ALL SERVICES OPERATIONAL</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"High Density\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: High Density\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"bg-slate-50 w-[1024px] h-[768px] flex flex-col font-sans overflow-hidden text-slate-900\\\">\\n  <!-- Header: Civic Status Bar -->\\n  <header class=\\\"h-14 bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-